----------------------------------------------------------------------------
This directory contains the standard corpus and early results for the
Spanish-English EuTrans-I (benchmark) data.

  The organization is as follows:

  FILES:
    00README: this file.
    training: the file containing the first 10,000 pairs of sentences
       of the standard EuTrans-I corpus (partition 1), including repetitions.
    test: 3,000 pairs from EuTrans-I. They include no repetitions and do not 
       overlap with the training.  The test sentences contain a few words NOT 
       included in training.
    test_closed (2,996 pairs): The same as test, but excluding the only four 
       lines that contain words NOT included in training.

  DIRECTORIES:
    voc: vocabularies of training and test data.

............................................................................
